guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-lai-marshall-islands-first-overseas-state-visit-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>内部备忘录称嘉吉计划在全球裁员约 5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/cargill-plans-cut-around-5-global-employees-internal-memo-says-2024-12-03/</link><description>路透社周二看到的一份内部备忘录显示，全球贸易公司嘉吉计划在全球范围内裁员 5% 左右。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 01:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/cargill-plans-cut-around-5-global-employees-internal-memo-says-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>公司表示，埃克森美孚在圭亚那拍卖中继续就浅水区块进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-talks-continue-shallow-water-block-guyana-auction-company-says-2024-12-03/</link><description>埃克森美孚发言人周一表示，美国石油巨头埃克森美孚及其合作伙伴正在继续与圭亚那政府就开发浅水石油区块的条款进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 00:48:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-talks-continue-shallow-water-block-guyana-auction-company-says-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>台湾抱怨后加拿大称太平洋贸易协定向新成员开放</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-says-pacific-trade-pact-open-new-members-after-taiwan-complains-2024-12-03/</link><description>加拿大政府表示，一项主要的跨太平洋贸易协定仍然向包括台湾在内的其他有抱负的成员开放，此前台湾抱怨尚未成立一个工作组来考虑其加入。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 00:40:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-says-pacific-trade-pact-open-new-members-after-taiwan-complains-2024-12-03/</guid></item><item><title>SEC 与 ICBC 部门就勒索软件攻击达成和解，但未处以罚款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/sec-settles-with-icbc-unit-over-ransomware-attack-imposes-no-fine-2024-12-02/</link><description>美国证券交易委员会已就 2023 年 11 月勒索软件攻击对中国工商银行一家子公司的记录保存指控达成和解，但决定不处以民事罚款。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 22:49:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/sec-settles-with-icbc-unit-over-ransomware-attack-imposes-no-fine-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：美元走强抑制多头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-02/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 21:48:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国无人机制造商更换五角大楼案件律师，放弃洛雷塔·林奇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/government/chinese-drone-maker-changes-lawyers-pentagon-case-dropping-loretta-lynch-2024-12-02/</link><description>中国无人机制造商大疆创新在针对美国国防部的诉讼中更换了其法律团队，将奥巴马时代的美国司法部长洛雷塔·林奇及其法律团队替换为奎因·伊曼纽尔·厄克特沙利文律师事务所的新律师。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 20:07:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/government/chinese-drone-maker-changes-lawyers-pentagon-case-dropping-loretta-lynch-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国对中国芯片产业实施新限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-targets-chinas-chip-industry-with-new-restrictions-2024-12-02/</link><description>美国周一对中国半导体行业发起了三年来的第三次严厉打击，限制了对包括芯片设备制造商北方华创科技集团在内的 140 家公司的出口。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 19:21:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-targets-chinas-chip-industry-with-new-restrictions-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>报告称中国激光雷达传感器对美国国防设备构成黑客风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-lidar-sensors-pose-hacking-risk-us-defense-equipment-report-says-2024-12-02/</link><description>华盛顿智库周一发布的报告称，中国制造的激光雷达传感器可能会使美国军方在冲突期间遭受黑客攻击和破坏，该报告呼吁禁止将这些传感器安装到美国国防设备中。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 15:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-lidar-sensors-pose-hacking-risk-us-defense-equipment-report-says-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国移动拟以 8.82 亿美元收购香港宽带网络</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kongs-hkbn-gets-rival-takeover-interest-i-squared-capital-2024-12-02/</link><description>中国移动周一表示，已提出收购香港宽频 (HKBN)，该交易对这家香港宽带公司的估值为 68.6 亿港元（合 8.82 亿美元），旨在对抗一家私募股权公司的举动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 09:40:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kongs-hkbn-gets-rival-takeover-interest-i-squared-capital-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔能源公司与壳牌签署向中国交付液化天然气的长期协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/qatarenergy-signs-long-term-lng-deal-with-shell-delivery-china-2024-12-02/</link><description>国有卡塔尔能源公司 (QATPE.UL) 与石油和天然气巨头壳牌公司签署了一项长期销售和采购协议，为其提供液化天然气 (LNG) 并运往中国，</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 09:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/qatarenergy-signs-long-term-lng-deal-with-shell-delivery-china-2024-12-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国债券持续上涨，10年期国债收益率跌破2%，创历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-relentless-bond-rally-pushes-10-year-yield-below-2-lowest-record-2024-12-02/</link><description>中国10年期国债收益率周一跌破2%，触及历史最低点，打破了心理障碍，因为经济不景气和进一步降息的押注促使投资者转向安全的债券。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 08:06:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-relentless-bond-rally-pushes-10-year-yield-below-2-lowest-record-2024-12-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>